item.title: CVE-2022-4790|2024-08-03T01:48:40.412Z -- unknown -- wp%20google%20my%20business%20auto%20publish
item.description: The WP Google My Business Auto Publish WordPress plugin before 3.4 does not validate and escape one of its shortcode attributes, which could allow users with a role as low as contributor to perform Stored Cross-Site Scripting attack.
